Templates use JSON format with the following key components:

```json
{
  "name": "Template Name",
  "description": "Template purpose",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "variables": {
    "input_data": "Data to process",
    "output_format": "Desired output format"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "step1",
      "name": "Process Input",
      "instruction": "Process {{input_data}}",
      "condition": "if input_data exists"
    }
  ]
}
```
